    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Short backswords, bayonets or choppers with a saw-back. Used by practically all armies during the 19th century, more often as a tool than as a weapon. Some fighting and survival knives are made as saw-backed knives.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
